reviewText: Two great films, one I like but I wouldn't say is great, all in one package! Being a huge Connery fan when I saw this box set of sorts I jumped on it. I LOVE The Hunt For Red October and The Untouchables, have and will continue to watch them over and over again. The Presidio is a pretty good movie in itself but I can't say it is as good as the other two.
summary: A Sean Connery fans must have!
